  "text": "Recent agricultural economics literature on poverty traps (see [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] Santos and Barrett, 2005) describes bifurcated wealth dynamics: households fall into one of two different 'clubs', separated by threshold lines above which asset accumulation occurs and below which a cycle of poverty reigns.",
